data.name: SAFETYCLOSE-SYSTEM IV CANNULA 2-WAYS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- 100% medical grade stainless steel
- Polypropylene (PP) and K-Resign Body
- Polypropylene (PP) and K-Resign Filter and Robert Clamp
- Polyurethane (PUR) Catheter
- PVC and DEHP-Free Tubing

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Closed System => 1- and 2-Ways Extension tube
- Color-Coded Size Identification
- Stripped and Full X-Ray Detectable Catheter’s Finish
- Hydrophobic Filter

## PERFORMANCE
- 3 bevelled + 2 Back Cuts Sharpness Technology
- Easy PASSIVE Activation Sliding Safety Mechanism
- inviolable closure technology
- Soft and anti-slip Surface colored Fixiation Wings
- Bevel Orientation Indicator
- Thin wall technology => High Flow
- Automatic Lubrication’s Technology => Optimal result on penetration resistance
- Smooth Surface
